),(17,'I take a consistent day off that ministry does not invade.','Rest, Rhythm & Health',true,false,'standard'),(18,'I take care of my physical health: sleep, movement, and eating.','Rest, Rhythm & Health',true,false,'standard'),(19,'I take my time away and vacation without guilt.','Rest, Rhythm & Health',true,false,'standard'),(20,'I am running on empty more often than not.','Rest, Rhythm & Health',true,true,'reverse'),(21,'My marriage is healthy and a source of strength.','Marriage & Family',true,false,'standard'),(22,'My family gets my best, not just my leftovers.','Marriage & Family',true,false,'standard'),(23,'My spouse and I are united in the ministry.','Marriage & Family',true,false,'standard'),(24,'Ministry regularly costs my family more than we have agreed to.','Marriage & Family',true,true,'reverse'),(25,'I preach and teach in a way that helps people understand and grow.','Preaching & Teaching',true,false,'standard'),(26,'I handle Scripture faithfully and accurately.','Preaching & Teaching',true,false,'standard'),(27,'People tell me my teaching has changed how they live.','Preaching & Teaching',true,false,'standard'),(28,'I keep growing as a communicator.','Preaching & Teaching',true,false,'standard'),(29,'I genuinely love and care for the people I lead.','Pastoral Care & Shepherding',true,false,'standard'),(30,'People come to me in crisis and leave helped.','Pastoral Care & Shepherding',true,false,'standard'),(31,'I balance caring for people with leading them.','Pastoral Care & Shepherding',true,false,'standard'),(32,'I find it hard to carry people''s burdens without being crushed by them.','Pastoral Care & Shepherding',true,true,'reverse'),(33,'I set a clear direction and move people toward it.','Leadership & Vision',true,false,'standard'),(34,'I develop and release other leaders.','Leadership & Vision',true,false,'standard'),(35,'I can make hard decisions when they are needed.','Leadership & Vision',true,false,'standard'),(36,'People follow my leadership willingly.','Leadership & Vision',true,false,'standard'),(37,'I face conflict directly rather than avoiding it.','Conflict Resolution',true,false,'standard'),(38,'I stay calm and non-defensive when I''m criticized.','Conflict Resolution',true,false,'standard'),(39,'I help people in conflict move toward real resolution.','Conflict Resolution',true,false,'standard'),(40,'I tend to avoid hard conversations until they blow up.','Conflict Resolution',true,true,'reverse'),(41,'I communicate clearly and listen well.','Communication & Relationships',true,false,'standard'),(42,'I build healthy relationships across the church.','Communication & Relationships',true,false,'standard'),(43,'I keep short accounts and repair relationships quickly.','Communication & Relationships',true,false,'standard'),(44,'People sometimes find me harder to reach than I intend.','Communication & Relationships',true,true,'reverse'),(45,'I intentionally make disciples, not just attract a crowd.','Disciple-Making & Multiplication',true,false,'standard'),(46,'I have a clear pathway that moves people toward maturity.','Disciple-Making & Multiplication',true,false,'standard'),(47,'The people I lead are beginning to reproduce in others.','Disciple-Making & Multiplication',true,false,'standard'),(48,'I actively seek input from people further along than me.','Mentoring & Accountability',true,false,'standard'),(49,'I am intentionally raising up the next generation of leaders.','Mentoring & Accountability',true,false,'standard'),(50,'I mostly carry ministry alone, without close accountability.','Mentoring & Accountability',true,true,'reverse'),(51,'I keep the church focused outward, not just inward.','Mission & Evangelism',true,false,'standard'),(52,'I personally engage people who are far from God.','Mission & Evangelism',true,false,'standard'),(53,'We are reaching new people, not just circulating existing ones.','Mission & Evangelism',true,false,'standard'),(54,'I''ve had little interest or joy in things I usually enjoy.','Wellbeing',true,false,'safety_check'),(55,'I''ve felt down, discouraged, or hopeless.','Wellbeing',true,false,'safety_check'),(56,'I''ve felt exhausted or drained, even after rest.','Wellbeing',true,false,'safety_check'),(57,'I''ve felt overwhelmed by the weight of ministry.','Wellbeing',true,false,'safety_check'),(58,'My sleep has been off, too little or too much.','Wellbeing',true,false,'safety_check'),(59,'I''ve felt alone, like no one really knows what I''m carrying.','Wellbeing',true,false,'safety_check'),(60,'I''ve felt like I''m just going through the motions with God.','Wellbeing',true,false,'safety_check'),(61,'I''ve wondered whether I can keep going.','Wellbeing',true,false,'safety_check')) as v(ord,txt,dom,sc,rev,it);
